Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kyoko? Kau sudah pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.68,0:00:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu ibuku! Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanakusa, sembunyilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan berisik!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jawab Ibu kalau kau ada di rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf! Aku tadi asyik membaca buku.\NJadi, aku tak mendengar Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahmu sudah pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Aku tak tahu, kurasa belum...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang! Kau sudah pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum! Sepatunya saja tak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tak ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, aku panik.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lemarimu cukup nyaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya kau Doraemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak, bagaimana dengan sepatuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kusembunyikan sepatumu\Ndi balik lemari sepatu untuk berjaga-jaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kenapa ekspresimu begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau seperti terduga yang mencoba\Nmenyembunyikan barang bukti.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Adik kelas kurang ajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.61,0:01:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa memahami jalan pikiran terduga\Nadalah cara tercepat memecahkan kasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu memang salah satu cara.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi nyaris saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, nyaris saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita panik sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat panik.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana ada detektif,\Ndi situ ada pengintaian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di seberang kantor ayahku ada kafe ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}benar-benar tempat yang cocok\Nuntuk berselingkuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bukan dialog yang cocok untuk orang\Nyang mengusut perselingkuhan ayahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertanyaan ini mungkin kurang ajar,\Ntapi kenapa selingkuh itu buruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebab pernikahan adalah kontrak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, orang yang melanggar kontrak\Npantas dikutuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak suka saja
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}jika dia lebih peduli wanita lain\Ndaripada keluarganya sendiri{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}atau jika melihat orang tuaku bertengkar...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku tak mau membayangkan\Nmasa persidangan yang melelahkan.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku memang sulit berteman. Jadi, rumahku...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}keluargaku sangat berarti bagiku.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti katamu tadi, Nanakusa.\NKurasa aku dibesarkan dengan kasih sayang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya aku merasa mual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisa dimaafkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar-benar gawat\Nkarena kau sampai mual begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menjadi jengkel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahmu selingkuh atau tidak,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia tetap sudah mencuri rumah\Ntempatmu kembali!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita rebut kembali rumahmu\Ndengan menjadi detektif!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanakusa, aku sudah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahku
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}baru saja masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat sembunyi ke bawah meja\Nsekarang, Kak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa?\N- Cepat sembunyi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana di bawah situ, Kak?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kursinya lumayan jauh, Kak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kurasa lebih baik kau di bawah saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, aku tak keberatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahmu masih terus bekerja\Nmeski sudah pulang dari kantor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah, dia sangat berdedikasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika dia sendirian begini,\Nmungkin wanitanya bukan rekan kerjanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bermain detektif seperti ini seru juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya masalah keluargaku ini\Nmenjadi hiburan bagimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus awasi dia, Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Aku Watson?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum ada perkembangan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia melihat ponselnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia melihat, lalu memencet tombol-tombol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mengirim pesan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak, dia keluar dari kafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku harus membuntutinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu tadi? Aku terbentur sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku kehilangan jejaknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tanganmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia naik taksi, lalu aku tersandung\Nketika mengejarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanakusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, ulurkan tanganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus membasuhnya dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Lukamu sudah hampir sembuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya memang begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak, dengarkan aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya aku bukan manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan manusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika bukan manusia, lantas apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Vampir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:18.06,tanda,,0,0,0,,KAFE KOMIK DAN INTERNET
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku terlihat baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak baik-baik saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu dengan vampir?\NKau mengisap darah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa bedanya dari manusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku bertanya serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pun tak tahu.\NAku tak ingat masa-masa manusiaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tak pernah berinteraksi\Ndengan vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia menjadi vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin semuanya dulu manusia,\Nkecuali vampir yang pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa menjadi vampir juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku penasaran saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya ada satu syarat,\Nkau harus jatuh cinta dengan vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jatuh cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Berarti itu mustahil karena kau sepertinya\Ntak bisa jatuh cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Benar juga, tapi kalimatmu\Nterdengar menjengkelkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau memang benar. Jatuh cinta\Npada manusia saja aku tak bisa,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa lagi dengan vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski vampirnya itu aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata kau memang vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mataharinya cerah sekali\Ndan tubuhku terasa sangat berat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau manis sekali,\Nseperti artis zaman dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kenapa kau berseragam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku mau ke sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku harus ambil tas sekolahku dulu\Ndari rumah,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi entah bagaimana caraku menjelaskan\Naku keluar semalaman tanpa izin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Perasaanku campur aduk.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kasihan manusia.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Kak.\NAku mau mengembalikan pakaianmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa melihat dengan kacamata itu\Ndi malam hari?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sebenarnya tak bisa melihat apa-apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana? Kau dimarahi habis-habisan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah? Baguslah kalau begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka tak bicara sepatah kata pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putri semata wayang mereka\Nyang berusia 17 tahun pergi semalaman,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi mereka tak bicara\Nsepatah kata pun padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya ayahku belum juga pulang\Nsetelah dari kafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya, ibuku terus mengomel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya ibuku tak peduli padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hatiku selalu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hatiku selalu hancur, tapi aku tak punya\Nteman untuk tempat bercerita.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun aku bercerita,\Nmereka selalu menganggapnya remeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setiap keluarga pasti punya masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi hatiku sakit sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Haruskah aku hidup\Ndengan rasa sakit ini selamanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanakusa, apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kak. Apa yang bisa kulakukan untuknya?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tak menjadi keturunanku saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:11:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tinggalkan semuanya\Ndan jatuh cintalah denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menemanimu selamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jatuh cinta denganmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Tidak ada manusia yang sebodoh itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.85,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\an8}RANTAI CINTA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yakin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat yakin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bolehkah aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Isaplah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak butuh keturunan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andaipun aku hidup seorang diri,\Ntak punya kawanan, lalu mati kebosanan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak keberatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku merasa\Nmau berbuat sesuatu untuknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terasa menyengat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga, vampir tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kami tak muncul di cermin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi entah kenapa, aku merasa segar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pertama kalinya aku mengisap manusia\Nyang sadar, jadi rasanya aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Lalu, bagaimana caramu mengisap darah\Nselama ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kuisap darah para pemabuk yang tidur\Ndi kursi taman. Sedikit-sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku tak pernah mau punya keturunan\Nkarena pasti akan merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya kupikir kau bisa menjadi\Nketurunanku yang pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku menciummu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti, jika aku mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa ekspresimu begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, sampai jumpa lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau kuantarkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tinggi! Ini tinggi sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tinggi, 'kan? Bagaimana, Kak Mejiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini mengerikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakiku sampai gemetaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi seru, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yakin, Kak?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat yakin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, sampai jumpa lagi\Npukul 02.00 nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kyo Sayang, selamat datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahmu mau bicara denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah minta maaf atas segalanya, Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah insaf. Ayah akan mengutamakanmu\Ndan ibumu mulai sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang Ayah bilang?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah punya wanita simpanan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Ayah sudah putus dengannya\Nkarena sadar apa yang paling penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu juga mau minta maaf, Kyo Sayang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebab Ibu belakangan ini bertingkah aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu tak begitu memperhatikanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu sadar seharusnya\Ntetap memperhatikanmu, apa pun itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua itu sudah terlambat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kyo Sayang!\N- Kyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:15:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah, Ibu, aku sangat kesepian...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.07,tanda,,0,0,0,,SELAMAT ULANG TAHUN
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Ulang tahunku hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, tanggal 31 Oktober,\Nbertepatan dengan Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah cepat-cepat membeli kue ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kyoko terlihat tegar dari luar,\Ntapi dia ternyata cengeng juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal ketika bertengkar\Ndengan laki-laki,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau bisa menahan air matamu\Nsampai ke rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh kutiup lilinnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiuplah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat ulang tahun\Nyang ke-18, Kyo Sayang!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau hadiah apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak butuh apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asalkan Ayah sudah kembali, aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana nasib pemantik pemberianku\Nuntuk Ayah itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah tak mau memakainya? Ayah tak suka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kyoko, sebentar, bukan begitu maksudnya.\NDengar Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya sayang...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah takut pemantiknya hilang
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena Ayah senang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ini momen yang bagus.\NJadi, Ayah pakai saja pemantiknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi jangan pernah menyalakan rokok\Nuntuk orang lain selain Ayah, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, rokoknya terasa beda dari biasanya.\NAyah ambil yang lain saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa, Ayah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pegang baik-baik, Yah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh! Ada apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kyoko terluka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kau yang memukulnya?\N- Bu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pukul wajah putrimu sendiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa? Katakan padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau akhirnya pulang dan minta maaf!\NPadahal aku percaya padamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pun tak luput dari kesalahan!\NMakanya kita sepakat untuk memulai lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan diam saja, Sayang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang? Siapa?\NItu bukan aku. Bukan milikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak akan pernah berpikir begitu!\NMereka orang asing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku! Karena aku mencintaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kenapa aku berbuat seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak pernah terpikir\Nmau minum darah sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aneh.\N- Darah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ini hanya mimpi? Mungkin juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Sayang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}- Dia mati?\N- Ibu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Berarti ini mimpi.\NTidak apa jika ini hanya mimpi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Vampir...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus pastikan yang berikutnya\Ntak akan sampai mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ini hanya mimpi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, tak apa-apa jika dia mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu ini hanya mimpi!\NJadi, tak akan sakit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dari mana awal mimpi ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu mau punya kamar sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa? Ini...\N- Nanakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin kau bisa saja membunuhku saat itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini ulah vam...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jawab aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa membunuh orang\Ndengan mengisap darahnya, 'kan?
